## Best Practices

### Task Organization
- Group related tasks together
- Use clear, actionable task descriptions
- Break large tasks into smaller, manageable pieces
- Prioritize tasks by importance and dependencies

### Progress Tracking
- Update task status regularly
- Document decisions and changes
- Keep implementation details current
- Note any blockers or issues

### File Management
- Keep file paths accurate and up-to-date
- Add descriptions for each file's purpose
- Mark completed components with status indicators
- Include relevant configuration files

### Collaboration
- Use consistent formatting across task lists
- Include context for complex features
- Document architectural decisions
- Share progress updates clearly
